{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5fcdff71-a654-47db-998c-cd131e0a35c8","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter by default.** Starting with v4.0, MSTest.Sdk exclusively uses **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** as the runner and no longer ships the VSTest bridge. Since `vstest.console` relies on that adapter to discover tests, it finds nothing.\n\nYou have two options:\n\n### Option 1 — Switch your CI to `dotnet test` (recommended)\n`dotnet test` in .NET 8+ natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform. No project changes needed.\n\n### Option 2 — Re-enable the VSTest bridge\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>\n```\n\nThis restores the adapter so `vstest.console` can discover tests again, but it's considered a compatibility shim, not the long-term path.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bfe94b65-3f43-4944-93f0-4e97eba66278","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, MSTest moved toward Microsoft.Testing.Platform as the default runner. In MSTest.Sdk 4.0+, the VSTest compatibility layer (the VSTest runner/adapter) is no longer included by default. This means `vstest.console.exe` (and `dotnet test` in its older VSTest mode) can no longer discover or run tests unless you explicitly opt back in.\n\nThe key change: MSTest.Sdk 4.x sets `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` by default and no longer ships the VSTest adapter. \n\nSince `vstest.console` depends on that adapter to find tests, it fails when it's missing. I can fix this by switching to `dotnet test` with .NET 8+, re-enabling the VSTest bridge with `<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>`, or running the native test executable directly.","outputTokens":552,"requestId":"5C43:2582EE:49705B:5C4FFF:69F56523"},"id":"b0634d1f-b11f-4286-ba4f-020c58462464","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:45:03.751Z","parentId":"cd614600-53c4-4d92-bbb7-b8bab9a9d2d6"}
